To install puppet from scratch:
sudo yum -y install git
git clone http://bornready:Test12345@github.com/bornready/orville
sudo cp orville/yum.repos.d/puppet.repo /etc/yum.repos.d/
sudo yum -y --enablerepo=puppetlabs install puppet

Instructions for adding a puppet rvm module
https://github.com/blt04/puppet-rvm


